---
layout: default
---
<div class="home">
    <style scoped>
        {% assign image = site.header_feature_image | relative_url | split: '.' %}
        .call-out_img {
            background-image: url('{{ image | join: '.' }}');
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px; /* Adjust padding as needed */
            background-size: 100% 100%; /* Set the width to 100% and the height to 100% */
            background-position: center;
            min-height: 50vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        {% if site.header_feature_image_responsive %}
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .call-out_img {
                background-image: url('{{ image[0] | append: '-medium.' | append: image[1] | default: image}}');
            }
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 576px) {
            .call-out_img {
                background-image: url('{{ image[0] | append: '-small.' | append: image[1] }}');
            }
        }
        {% endif %}
        .text-box {
            position: relative;
            top: 40px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 700px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border: 0px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #2171b5;
            font-family: 'Avenir Next LT Pro';
        }
    </style>
    <div id="main" class="call-out call-out_img">
        <h1>{{ site.header_text | default: ""}}</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Text box -->
    <div class="text-box">
        <p>
            As a physicist, I develop mathematical models and utilize computer simulations to study material properties for nanoelectronic applications. In addition to computational work on materials, I have also used optical interferometric microscopy to characterize the surface topography of solar cells and optical flats. Finally, I am proud to highlight my solid foundation in data analytics, using data science, machine learning, and optimization techniques throughout my academic career.
        </p>
    </div>

    {% capture _blog %}{% include blog/blog.liquid %}{% endcapture %}
    {{ _blog | split: " " | join: " "}}
</div>
